# PowerShell config
# Ignore poweshell modules
/.config/powershell/Modules
# Ignore the standard per-machine configuration
# See: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/scripting/learn/shell/creating-profiles?view=powershell-7.6#the-profile-variable
